   SIERRALEONE-U.N. (United Nations) _ Human rights groups are
campaigning against a blanket amnesty in Sierra Leone that granted
pardons for rebel leaders considered responsible for a campaign to
mutiliate civilians. By Paul Lewis.
</P>
<P>
   PAKISTAN-JOURNALIST (Lahore) _ The arrest, subsequent release,
and harassment of Pakistan's pluckiest journalist. By Celia Dugger.
